{
  "id": "adv_event_2503_01_01",
  "title": "SOS団、\n緊急会議！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_northschoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、怜ちゃん発見～！　一緒に部室行こ！\nハルヒちゃんがSOS団緊急会議をするんだって～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あ、怜ちゃん発見～！　一緒に部室行こ！\nハルヒちゃんがSOS団緊急会議をするんだって～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.6329027176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_northschoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 3.6936665557
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_northschoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 9.8448529561
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっとどういうこと？　今日は活動日じゃない\nはずよ。そもそも芽衣はSOS団の団員じゃないでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ちょ、ちょっとどういうこと？　今日は活動日じゃない\nはずよ。そもそも芽衣はSOS団の団員じゃないでしょ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8448529561,
      "endTime": 19.27054437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_northschoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.4824946086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "だから緊急会議なんだって！　それに、実はなんと！\nちょうどさっき芽衣もSOS団の団員になったんだー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "だから緊急会議なんだって！　それに、実はなんと！\nちょうどさっき芽衣もSOS団の団員になったんだー！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4824946086,
      "endTime": 29.2324944179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_northschoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 29.4444446564
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "トイレで幽霊さん達とお話ししてたらハルヒちゃんに\n霊能力者？　に間違われてスカウトされたんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "トイレで幽霊さん達とお話ししてたらハルヒちゃんに\n霊能力者？　に間違われてスカウトされたんだよね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4444446564,
      "endTime": 37.9225624085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、霊能力者じゃないんだけど\nなんか面白そうだから入ることにしたんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "芽衣、霊能力者じゃないんだけど\nなんか面白そうだから入ることにしたんだ～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.134512647,
      "endTime": 44.4007711728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_northschoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 44.6127214114
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "あー……いろいろとツッコミたいところはあるけれど\nハルヒらしい勧誘の仕方ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あー……いろいろとツッコミたいところはあるけれど\nハルヒらしい勧誘の仕方ね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6127214114,
      "endTime": 53.228140608400004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_northschoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 53.440090847
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "……って、早く早く！　もうハルヒちゃん達\n待ってるんだから立ち話なんてしてる暇ないよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……って、早く早く！　もうハルヒちゃん達\n待ってるんだから立ち話なんてしてる暇ないよー！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.440090847,
      "endTime": 60.6494784355,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-03.m4a",
          "delay": 8621.337826999998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_northschoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 55.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "haruhi",
      "speakerName": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "speakerNameEn": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruhi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-haruhi001.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも遅ーいっ！　遅刻よ、遅刻！\nぼさっと突っ立ってないで早く入りなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "二人とも遅ーいっ！　遅刻よ、遅刻！\nぼさっと突っ立ってないで早く入りなさい",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.861428674,
      "endTime": 69.38281176880001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣から聞いたけど、緊急会議ってどういうこと？\n今日は活動日じゃなかったはずよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "芽衣から聞いたけど、緊急会議ってどういうこと？\n今日は活動日じゃなかったはずよね……？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5947620074,
      "endTime": 76.6399545351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mikuru",
      "speakerName": "朝比奈みくる",
      "speakerNameEn": "朝比奈みくる",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mikuru.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-mikuru001.m4a",
      "text": "明後日、地元のお祭りに出展する出店に関して\n涼宮さんから、大事な報告があるそうですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "明後日、地元のお祭りに出展する出店に関して\n涼宮さんから、大事な報告があるそうですよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8519047737,
      "endTime": 86.3849436759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "一体何をするつもりなんだろう？　詳細を聞かずに\n付いて来ちゃったけど、私しっかり手伝えるかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "一体何をするつもりなんだろう？　詳細を聞かずに\n付いて来ちゃったけど、私しっかり手伝えるかな……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.585238107,
      "endTime": 96.3654646237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "って、千紗！？　なんであなたがここにいるのよ！\nなんか沙季もいるし。急に団員が増え過ぎじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "って、千紗！？　なんであなたがここにいるのよ！\nなんか沙季もいるし。急に団員が増え過ぎじゃない？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5774148623,
      "endTime": 104.69956890739999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yuki",
      "speakerName": "長門有希",
      "speakerNameEn": "長門有希",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yuki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-yuki001.m4a",
      "text": "問題ない。部室の広さ的にもまだ増やせる\n涼宮ハルヒが連れて来たのならば受け入れるべき",
      "translations": {
        "en": "問題ない。部室の広さ的にもまだ増やせる\n涼宮ハルヒが連れて来たのならば受け入れるべき",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9115191459,
      "endTime": 114.6325396537,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことを言ってるんじゃないのだけれど……\nはぁ、有希に言っても通じなそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そういうことを言ってるんじゃないのだけれど……\nはぁ、有希に言っても通じなそうね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8448524792,
      "endTime": 122.9083445866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "haruhi",
      "speakerName": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "speakerNameEn": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruhi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-haruhi002.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！　千紗ちゃんはさっき手芸部で捕まえたのよ\nちょうど小動物系のマスコットが欲しかったのよねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そうそう！　千紗ちゃんはさっき手芸部で捕まえたのよ\nちょうど小動物系のマスコットが欲しかったのよねー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1202948252,
      "endTime": 130.1804080645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、捕まえた……？　たとえ涼宮さんであろうとも\n千紗に手荒な真似をしたら許しませんからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ふふっ、捕まえた……？　たとえ涼宮さんであろうとも\n千紗に手荒な真似をしたら許しませんからね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3869614918,
      "endTime": 139.7543309528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "haruhi",
      "speakerName": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "speakerNameEn": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruhi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-haruhi003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことする訳ないでしょ。SOS団マスコット\n第一号に聞いてみなさいよ。ね、みくるちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そんなことする訳ないでしょ。SOS団マスコット\n第一号に聞いてみなさいよ。ね、みくるちゃん？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.9662811915,
      "endTime": 147.5877323786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mikuru",
      "speakerName": "朝比奈みくる",
      "speakerNameEn": "朝比奈みくる",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mikuru.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-mikuru002.m4a",
      "text": "はわぁ……っ！？　沙季さんの顔がこ、怖いですぅ\nわ、わたしはどうしたら……えっと……うーんと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はわぁ……っ！？　沙季さんの顔がこ、怖いですぅ\nわ、わたしはどうしたら……えっと……うーんと……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7996145248,
      "endTime": 158.2762807846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "haruhi",
      "speakerName": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "speakerNameEn": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruhi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-haruhi004.m4a",
      "text": "あたしただの人間には興味ないんだけど、新団員に\nツンデレ担当の怜ちゃんに霊能力者の芽衣ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あたしただの人間には興味ないんだけど、新団員に\nツンデレ担当の怜ちゃんに霊能力者の芽衣ちゃん",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.4662811915,
      "endTime": 166.176825587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "haruhi",
      "speakerName": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "speakerNameEn": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruhi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-haruhi005.m4a",
      "text": "小動物担当の千紗ちゃん。そしてセットで優等生キャラ\nの沙季ちゃんまでゲット出来るなんてついてるわよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "小動物担当の千紗ちゃん。そしてセットで優等生キャラ\nの沙季ちゃんまでゲット出来るなんてついてるわよね！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.3662811915,
      "endTime": 173.99854895270002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ハルヒさんの圧に押されて付いて来ただけで、まだ\n団員になった訳じゃ……そもそもSOS団って……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ハルヒさんの圧に押されて付いて来ただけで、まだ\n団員になった訳じゃ……そもそもSOS団って……？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.1996145248,
      "endTime": 184.0343540191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "haruhi",
      "speakerName": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "speakerNameEn": "涼宮ハルヒ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruhi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2503_01_01-haruhi006.m4a",
      "text": "世界を大いに盛り上げるための涼宮ハルヒの団よ！\nてことで、お祭りのステージに立つことが決まったわ",
      "translations": {
